MathJax.Localization.addTranslation("vi","HelpDialog",{version:"2.7.9",isLoaded:!0,strings:{Help:"Tr\u1EE3 gi\xFAp MathJax",MathJax:"*MathJax* l\xE0 m\u1ED9t th\u01B0 vi\u1EC7n JavaScript cho ph\xE9p c\xE1c t\xE1c gi\u1EA3 nh\xFAng c\xF4ng th\u1EE9c to\xE1n h\u1ECDc v\xE0o trang Web. C\xE1c \u0111\u1ED9c gi\u1EA3 nh\u01B0 b\u1EA1n kh\xF4ng c\u1EA7n l\xE0m th\xEAm g\xEC \u0111\u1EC3 hi\u1EC3n th\u1ECB to\xE1n h\u1ECDc.",Browsers:"*Tr\xECnh duy\u1EC7t*: MathJax t\u01B0\u01A1ng th\xEDch v\u1EDBi t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c tr\xECnh duy\u1EC7t \u0111\u1EDDi m\u1EDBi, bao g\u1ED3m IE 6+, Firefox 3+, Chrome 0.2+, Safari 2+, Opera 9.6+, v\xE0 ph\u1EA7n nhi\u1EC1u tr\xECnh duy\u1EC7t di \u0111\u1ED9ng.",Menu:"*Tr\xECnh \u0111\u01A1n To\xE1n h\u1ECDc*: MathJax th\xEAm m\u1ED9t tr\xECnh \u0111\u01A1n ng\u1EEF c\u1EA3nh v\xE0o c\xE1c ph\u01B0\u01A1ng tr\xECnh. Nh\u1EA5n chu\u1ED9t ph\u1EA3i ho\u1EB7c nh\u1EA5n gi\u1EEF Ctrl v\xE0 nh\u1EA5n chu\u1ED9t tr\xE1i \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF tr\xECnh \u0111\u01A1n n\xE0y.",ShowMath:"*Xem To\xE1n D\u01B0\u1EDBi d\u1EA1ng* cho ph\xE9p xem v\xE0 ch\xE9p d\xE1n m\xE3 ngu\u1ED3n c\u1EE7a ph\u01B0\u01A1ng tr\xECnh (d\u01B0\u1EDBi d\u1EA1ng MathML ho\u1EB7c \u0111\u1ECBnh d\u1EA1ng g\u1ED1c).",Settings:"*T\xF9y ch\u1ECDn To\xE1n* cho ph\xE9p \u0111i\u1EC1u khi\u1EC3n c\xE1c t\xEDnh n\u0103ng c\u1EE7a MathJax, th\xED d\u1EE5 nh\u01B0 k\xEDch th\u01B0\u1EDBc k\xFD t\u1EF1 to\xE1n h\u1ECDc, c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 ph\u01B0\u01A1ng ph\xE1p hi\u1EC3n th\u1ECB c\xE1c ph\u01B0\u01A1ng tr\xECnh.",Language:"*Ng\xF4n ng\u1EEF* cho ph\xE9p l\u1EF1a ch\u1ECDn ng\xF4n ng\u1EEF cho c\xE1c tr\xECnh \u0111\u01A1n v\xE0 th\xF4ng \u0111i\u1EC7p trong MathJax.",Zoom:"*Ph\xF3ng to*: N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n c\u1EA3m th\u1EA5y kh\xF3 \u0111\u1ECDc m\u1ED9t ph\u01B0\u01A1ng tr\xECnh, MathJax c\xF3 th\u1EC3 ph\xF3ng to n\xF3 \u0111\u1EC3 gi\xFAp b\u1EA1n th\u1EA5y r\xF5 h\u01A1n.",Accessibilty:"*Tr\u1EE3 n\u0103ng*: MathJax t\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ED9ng t\xE1c \u0111\u1ED9ng v\u1EDBi c\xE1c tr\xECnh \u0111\u1ECDc m\xE0n h\xECnh \u0111\u1EC3 gi\xFAp ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\xF9 l\xF2a truy c\u1EADp to\xE1n h\u1ECDc.",Fonts:"*Ph\xF4ng ch\u1EEF*: MathJax s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 ph\xF4ng ch\u1EEF to\xE1n h\u1ECDc n\u1EBFu \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c c\xE0i \u0111\u1EB7t tr\xEAn m\xE1y c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n; n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng, n\xF3 t\u1EA3i c\xE1c ph\xF4ng ch\u1EEF Web. B\u1EA1n c\xF3 th\u1EC3 (nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng c\u1EA7n ph\u1EA3i) c\xE0i \u0111\u1EB7t c\xE1c ph\xF4ng ch\u1EEF v\xE0o m\xE1y \u0111\u1EC3 t\u0103ng t\u1ED1c \u0111\u1ED9 s\u1EAFp ch\u1EEF. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i khuy\u1EBFn kh\xEDch c\xE0i \u0111\u1EB7t c\xE1c [ph\xF4ng ch\u1EEF STIX](%1).",CloseDialog:"\u0110\xF3ng h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i tr\u1EE3 gi\xFAp"}}),MathJax.Ajax.loadComplete("[MathJax]/localization/vi/HelpDialog.js");
